author: bpendleton
msg: DERBY-4758: Add documentation for PlanExporter tool
This patch was contributed by C.S. Nirmal J. Fernando (nirmal070125 at gmail dot com)
This patch adds documentation for the PlanExporter tool to the Derby Tools
and Utilities guide. The initial version of the documentation describes
the purpose of the tools, the syntax for invoking the tool, and some examples
of how to run the tool to achieve a variety of output formats.

msg: * subversion/svnrdump/load_editor.c
(new_node_record): Remove incorrect comment about the historical
detail in the commit editor, and handle the svn_node_action actions/

implemented.

(close_node): Remove the close_file, close_directory calls from
here. It's incorrect to put them here.
(close_revision): Add a close_directory call corresponding to the
toplevel open_root.

only seemed to work by accident.
